CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 29, 1971, pg. 21, reads: "Meter Maid At Work - Mrs. Katie Mae Thomas performs typical duties of Meter Maids in Pittsburgh as she checks a meter for a violation and them proceeds to make some motorist unhappy by writing a ticket to place on his car. Those uniformed ladies aren't playing. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Meter Maid Katie Mae Howze Thomas writing parking ticket in front of Twentieth Century Club, Oakland
